The paper discusses a chaotic cryptosystem and its security, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the defect in the enhanced cryptosystem and proposes countermeasures, which involves system analysis and design (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
